Products Archive - Rockwell Collins










































 








Toggle navigation





Toggle Search



                Rockwell Collins              










Home Products 









View Products ›



Seating Products
Rockwell Collins designs and develops a complete line of commercial and business jet seating solutions, including main cabin, business class, super first class, and executive aircraft seating.
Learn More ›






View Products ›



Galley Systems
Rockwell Collins provides innovative galley structures and inserts that enable airlines to enhance the passenger experience.
Learn More ›






View Products ›



Structures & Integration
In addition to driving innovative solutions that maximize space, Rockwell Collins seamlessly integrates interiors for the optimum cabin upgrade and retrofit.
Learn More ›






View Products ›



Lighting & Integrated Systems
Rockwell Collins offers an optimum solution for airlines and lessors seeking a cost-effective way to enhance the cabin ambience.
Learn More ›






View Products ›



Oxygen & PSU Systems
Rockwell Collins is a world leader in providing safe and innovative crew, passenger, and PSU systems for commercial, business jet, and military airframes.
Learn More ›






View Products ›



Water & Waste Systems
Rockwell Collins’ advanced-design vacuum waste systems and components for commercial aircraft and business jets solve maintenance problems and cut costs.
Learn More ›






View Products ›



De-icing Systems
Ice Shield™ is a preferred brand of aircraft de-icers, with its highly effective performance and lab-proven longevity.
Learn More ›






View Products ›



Thermal and Power Management
Rockwell Collins is a market leader in the design, engineering, and manufacturing of customized, fully integrated, thermal management solutions.
Learn More ›






View Products ›



Electronic Systems
We engineer custom solutions for electronics, power, interconnect, data storage & processing systems, focusing on high performance and reduced volume/weight.
Learn More ›







