#IWantToBeRC


Rockwell Collins is an equal opportunity employer. All qualified applicants will receive consideration for employment and will not be discriminated against on the basis of race, gender, sexual orientation, gender identity, disability, protected veteran or any other protected status.
If you are applying for a job in the U.S. or Canada and need a reasonable accommodation for any part of the employment process, please email our Employee Service Center at employeeservice@rockwellcollins.com or call 1-866-295-4747, option 6, and let us know the nature of your request and contact information. Please note that only those inquiries concerning a request for reasonable accommodation will be responded to from this e-mail address and phone number.
Copyright ©   Rockwell Collins. All rights reserved. | Privacy & Cookies | To learn more, view the EEO poster and  Pay Transparency Poster.



















