B/E Aerospace - Wikipedia






















 






B/E Aerospace

From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia


					Jump to:					navigation, 					search

Not to be confused with BAE Systems.

B/E Aerospace, Inc.




Fate
Acquired


Founded
1987 as Bach Engineering[1]


Headquarters
Wellington, Florida, USA



Area served

Global



Key people

Amin Khoury, founder and Chairman


